      "message": "refactor: remove leftover compaction references\n\nThe stream compaction helper is unused, and the remaining benchmark comment about preventing compaction no longer matches the actual deserialization pattern.\n\nRemove `Compact()` and switch the `rpc_blockchain` fixture reader to `SpanReader`.\nThis drops the last leftover compaction workaround before the block deserialization benchmarks are updated as well.",
